        "template--16165595545778__17aa76ca-3d53-4eb9-850c-d949111d8309-heading-1": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "<strong>Premium Olive Oil from the Heart of Palestine</strong>",
            "heading_size": "h0"
          }
        },
        "template--16165595545778__17aa76ca-3d53-4eb9-850c-d949111d8309-text-1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>From the sun-kissed groves of Palestine, Al'Ard brings you a premium selection of award-winning <a href=\"/collections/palestinian-olive-oil\" title=\"Palestinian Olive Oil\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><strong>Palestinian olive oils</strong></span></a> —Extra Virgin, Organic, and Premium—cold-pressed using time-honored techniques to preserve their authentic flavor and rich heritage.</p><p>But Al’Ard offers more than olive oil. Our growing range includes traditional <a href=\"/collections/gift-card\" title=\"Palestinian Pantry\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><strong>Palestinian pantry</strong></span></a> : Maftoul & Freekah, <a href=\"/collections/gift-card\" title=\"Palestinian Pantry\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><strong>red chili sauce</strong></span></a>, aromatic spices, <a href=\"/collections/gift-card\" title=\"Palestinian Pantry\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\"><strong>premium pickles</strong></span></a>, Nabulsi products, and more—each crafted to reflect the depth of Palestinian culture and cuisine.</p><p>Now available across the UK, Al’Ard products are a celebration of quality, tradition, and the enduring connection to the land of Palestine.</p><p>Each item tells a story — of ancestral soil, generational care, and flavors that carry the soul of a people. With every jar, bottle, or grain, you bring a piece of Palestine into your home.</p>",
            "text_style": "subtitle"
          }
        },
