            "heading": "<strong>Palestinian Recipes</strong>",
            "heading_size": "h0"
          }
        },
        "template--16165595545778__74a01cbc-229e-4ff0-9deb-20e5a38b6085-text-1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Palestinian cuisine is a reflection of our rich history, culture, and heritage. It is a culinary journey that tantalizes the taste buds with an array of flavors and aromas, showcasing the bountiful ingredients of our land. From the iconic dishes like zaatar and hummus to lesser-known gems like maqluba and Msakhan, Palestinian cuisine is a celebration of fresh, locally sourced ingredients, handcrafted with love and care. Each bite tells a story, connecting you to the ancient traditions and warm hospitality of our people. Join us in savoring the authentic flavors of Palestine and experiencing the true essence of our vibrant culinary heritage.</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        },
